rows.label: qev042203_MSG0001
rows.name:
Oooooo, graaaaawl! It looks like Divine Napopon lost
to big, strong friend...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042203_MSG0002
rows.name:
[ST:playername ] is too strong. Toooo strong!
Mmmm...excitement...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042203_MSG0003
rows.name:
Divine Napopon love meeting big, strong friends...
even though it still sting to lose.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042203_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell the Divine Napopon that it was a fun fight, at least.

rows.label: qev042203_SEL0021
rows.name: Say that the fight wasn't fun for you at all.

rows.label: qev042203_MSG0004
rows.name:
Mmmm... Divine Napopon THIS close to having giant
crush on [ST:playername ]...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042203_MSG0005
rows.name:
But it is love forbidden! Instead, Divine Napopon will
keep it forever hidden away deep inside heart.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042203_MSG0006
rows.name:
Noooooo! Divine Napopon never wanted to cause
trouble for beautiful friend [ST:playername ]![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042203_MSG0007
rows.name: Divine Napopon feel so very terrible now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042203_MSG0008
rows.name:
Whole point was to show [ST:playername ]
good time. ...Way fun good time, if friend knows
what Divine Napopon means.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042203_MSG0010
rows.name:
Divine Napopon went ahead and blessed gemstone
[ST:playername ] brought.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042203_MSG0011
rows.name:
That makes friend one step closer to uncovering Nopon
origins.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev042203_MSG0013
rows.name:
Oh, and tell late bloomer Nopopon to hurry up and
find nice girl already.[ST:wait ]
